item.title: Float x P O W x Changes - aUstin Haga x HAYW1R3 x aUstin Haga (James Lucien's Epic Mashup Mix)
item.dc:creator: TheRealJFalc
item.description:
Against my better judgement, the track has been reinstated on my SC. I feel that it’s important to take a step back from music and just enjoy a song for what it is. If you’re too serious all the time… you’re going to lose out on the little moments. Like I did. I’m going to change that from now on.

https://soundcloud.com/james-lucien-official/austin-haga-hayw1r3-float-pow-changes-epic-mashup-mix

Thank you @aUstin_Haga for writing your songs and to HAYW1R3 for your song. They helped me grow and understand music a lot more, especially Float. I’m going to keep improving and making my music in new and exciting ways, and I won’t lose sight of what music is all about in the future.
